  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a bonus action, you can choose up to a creatures that you can see within 30 feet of you. At the start of the creature's next turn, the creature must use its Attack action (using multiple attacks if availble to it) against the nearest creature to them. If they are required to move to the their target then they use their movement to do so. The curse ends at the end of the creature's turn.</p><p>If more than one creature is equally near to you, roll randomly to determine your target.</p><p><strong>Amplify</strong>. The creature does whatever action would deal the most damage. The curse ends at the end of the creature's turn.</p>",
